org.beiter.michael.eaudit4j.common.propsbuilder

Class MapBasedCommonPropsBuilder

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.beiter.michael.eaudit4j.common.propsbuilder.MapBasedCommonPropsBuilder

  • public final class MapBasedCommonPropsBuilder
extends Object
    This class builds a set of CommonProperties using the settings obtained from a Map.

    Use the keys from the various KEY_* fields to properly populate the Map before calling this class' methods.
